c74object.name: fl.subframe~
c74object.digest: Output part of an input frame.
c74object.description: The subframe is specified by a start and end point in the input frame.

entry.name: 0. /start [double]
entry.description: Sets the start point of the subframe.

entry.name: 1. /end [double]
entry.description: Sets the end point of the subframe.

entry.name: 2. /units [enum]
entry.description:
Sets units for the start and end points (samples or ratios [0-1]).
[0] - samples [1] - ratios
